--- .gitignore (原始)
```
# Compiled and build artifacts
*.class
*.dex
*.so
*.aar
# Dependencies
.gradle/
build/
# Logs and temp files
*.log
*.tmp
# Environment
.env
.env.local
*.env.*
# Editors
.vscode/
.idea/
```

+++ .gitignore (修改后)
```kotlin
# Kotlin/Android build artifacts
*.class
*.dex
*.jar
*.aar
*.so
*.dll
*.dylib

# Android specific
build/
.gradle/
local.properties
captures/
.externalNativeBuild/

# IDE files
.idea/
*.iml
*.ipr
*.iws
.vscode/

# Gradle
.gradle/
gradle-app.setting

# Logs
*.log

# Temp files
*.tmp
*.temp

# Environment
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Coverage
coverage/
*.coverage
.htmlcov/

# Python (if any Python tools used in project)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
env/
venv/
.venv/

# Node (if any Node tools used in project)
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Compiled source
*.com
*.class
*.dll
*.exe
*.o
*.so

# Packages
*.7z
*.dmg
*.gz
*.iso
*.jar
*.rar
*.tar
*.zip

# System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
```
